news.title: Andhra Pradesh stands first in LED street lighting project
news.para: As the Energy Efficiency Services Limited commemorates the 9th anniversary of Ujala and SLNP, it has announced that 36.86 crore LED bulbs, 72.18 lakh tube lights, and 23.59 lakh energy-efficient fans have been supplied since its inception.

news.title: Hubballi-Dharwad civic body's LED streetlight scheme remains on paper
news.para: While HDMC has sanctioned funds for LED bulb installation in some wards, the project's full-scale implementation is pending, leaving certain areas without adequate number of street lights.

news.title: About 33 families facing eviction allotted Lucknow development body's flats
news.para: The LDA is evacuating residents of Akbarnagar because, as per the officials, the colony has been built on the Kukrail river bed in violation to National Green Tribunal norms, said officials.
